Docker image for Half-Life Dedicated Server

Build an image:

 make build

Launch Counter-Strike 1.6 server:

 docker run -it -p 27020:27015/udp --name cs hlds:alpha -console

Add admin:

 amx_addadmin "STEAM_0:1:123456789" "abcdefghijklmnopqrstu"

Stop the server:

 docker stop cs

Remove the server:

 docker rm cs